title: Teen Mom 2 Star Jenelle Evans Is Engaged!
text:
Jenelle Evans , of Teen Mom 2 fame, is engaged! 
The reality TV star announced it just a couple hours ago on her Instagram account with a picture (above) of her, her fiancé, and the ring! So cute!! 
And of her fiancé David Eason , Evans wrote in the caption: 
"We've decided on forever! #PerfectTiming" 
Awww! Cute!! 
Of course, this is just a few weeks after Jenelle gave birth to the couple's baby girl — so it's been a big year already for Miz Evans!!! Love it! 
So happy for these two — congrats on the big engagement!!
